data.name: Time Thief Winder
data.desc: You can detach 1 material from an Xyz Monster you control; Special Summon this card from your hand. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Time Thief" card from your Deck to your hand, except "Time Thief Winder". You can only use each effect of "Time Thief Winder" once per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
